## 5. Pseudocode Examples

### Example 1: Attendance Warning

```
IF attendance_percentage < 75
    SEND warning email to student
    NOTIFY faculty advisor
END IF
```

### Example 2: Scholarship Eligibility

```
IF GPA >= 8.5
AND attendance >= 85
AND fee_status = "Paid"
THEN
    scholarship_status = "Eligible"
ELSE
    scholarship_status = "Not Eligible"
END IF
```

### Example 3: Course Enrollment Validation

```
IF course_capacity > enrolled_students
    CREATE enrollment
ELSE
    DISPLAY "Course Full"
END IF
```

### Example 4: Fee Due Reminder

```
FOR each student
    IF fee_due_date is within 7 days
        SEND reminder email
    END IF
END FOR
```

